  09 Aug 2015; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> +ceph-0.80.9.ebuild,
  +ceph-0.80.10-r1.ebuild, +ceph-0.94.2-r1.ebuild, +ceph-9999.ebuild,
